Russian Oil Firms Challenge Jump in Flaring Fees, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-10-14T04:30:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/russian-oil-firms-challenge-jump-in-flaring-fees-vedomosti-says.html
Russian oil companies are preparing
to appeal collectively against a 22-fold increase in fees for
the burning of associated petroleum gas, Vedomosti  reported ,
citing two unidentified employees of the companies.  A letter from the oil companies will request that the
Ministry of Natural Resources increase the fees gradually over
the next two years, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran at 
 Jcorcoran13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  